  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK428">
<l>añcuva tañcāmai pētaimai yañcuva</l>
<l>tañca laṟivār toḻil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Not to fear what ought to be feared, is folly; it is the work of the wise to fear what should be feared.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
